OL,7,FMs Adedayo had falsely confessed to
OL,8,Fbeing responsible for the shortfalls
OL,9,Fat her post office in Kent to avoid
OL,10,Fthe risk of ending up in prison.
OL,12,FShe was eventually cleared of any
OL,13,Fwrongdoing in 2021.
OL,15,FA quote from the Post Office's
OL,16,Fsubmission was read out during the
OL,17,Fquestioning of the organisation's
OL,18,Fformer chair, Tim Parker, on Wednesday.
