OL,7,FMr Henry asked Mr Parker his view on
OL,8,Fthe Post Office "effectively branding
OL,9,F(Ms Adedayo) a criminal despite her
OL,10,Fconviction having been quashed".
OL,12,FQuoting the submission, he said: "The
OL,13,Finquiry will be aware that this (Ms
OL,14,FAdedayo's case) is the sole case study
OL,15,Fwhere the Post Office does not accept
OL,16,Fthat the conviction was unsafe".
