OL,7,FMr Parker was appointed chair of Post
OL,8,FOffice Ltd in October 2015 and held
OL,9,Fthe position until he resigned on
OL,10,FSeptember 30 2022.
OL,12,FHe joined the organisation in the
OL,13,Fmidst of an ongoing dispute between
OL,14,Fthe company and numerous sub-
OL,15,Fpostmasters regarding its Horizon
OL,16,Fcomputer system.
