OL,5,Cconviction
OL,7,FMore than 700 sub-postmasters were
OL,8,Fprosecuted by the Post Office and
OL,9,Fhanded criminal convictions between
OL,10,F1999 and 2015 as Fujitsu's faulty
OL,11,FHorizon IT system made it appear as
OL,12,Fthough money was missing at their
OL,13,Fbranches.
OL,15,FSpeaking at the inquiry on Wednesday,
OL,16,FMr Parker said: "Today I was toying
OL,17,Fwith making an opening statement.
OL,18,FStand up, you say, 'I'm deeply, deeply
OL,19,Fsorry' as many people have done, and
OL,20,Fthere ensued a discussion with people.
